        A map of keys to values where keys and values are both strings.

        Parameters:
        pairs - Pairs of key/values.
        _encoded -

        The original string representation, if known. If present, this exact string will be written instead of the content in pairs. This may differ from the calculated representation from pairs due to implementations which append a final ";".

        Note: this field is ignored by equals/hashcode methods.
